肯定句
I am...
You/we/they are...
he/she/it is...

be动词的缩写形式
I'm ...
You/we/they're...
he/she/it's...

否定句
I am not...
You/we/they are not...
he/she/it is not...

be动词的缩写形式
I'm not...
You/we/they aren't...
he/she/it isn't...

问句
Am I...? 我是不是...？
Are you/we/they...? 你是不是...？
Is he/she/it...? 他是不是...？

如果你用be动词，你只可以用形容词，名词，或者动词ing
I am tall
You aren't John
Is she eating?'''),
