('Time Prepositions', '''Time Prepositions

in + 年/月/不具体的时候/季节
I will go to Japan in 2021
There is no school in June
I wake up in the morning
It is hot in summer

on + 一个日
My birthday is on Tuesday
There is no school on Christmas

at + 具体的时候
I go to sleep at 3pm

from + 开始的时候 + to + 结束的时候
Class is from 3pm to 4pm'''),
('Present Continuous', '''Present Continuous 现在进行时

be doing
总是需要be动词，还有动词加ing。没有这些所有部分的句子是不对的

I am eating
我在吃饭
You are not going
你不再去
Is she sleeping
她在睡觉吗？

如果动词最后的字母是一个e，去e加ing
write - writing

有些动词必须把最后一个字母双写。
run - running
sit - sitting
swim - swimming'''),
('Like Doing', '''Like Doing 喜欢做什么

动词ing 必须用在下面的每个动词之后
love(爱), like(喜欢), don't like(不喜欢), hate(讨厌)

I like eating
She likes sleeping

You don't like writing
He doesn't like running

Does he like watching TV?
Do we like drawing?'''),
