('Be动词 past tense', '''Past Simple Be be动词的过去时

肯定句
I was...
You/we/they were...
he/she/it was...

否定句
I was not...
You/we/they were not...
he/she/it was not...

还有可能用be动词的缩写形式
I wasn't...
You/we/they weren't...
he/she/it wasn't...

问句
Was I...? 我是不是...？
Were you/we/they...? 你是不是...？
Was he/she/it...? 他是不是...？

如果你用be动词，你只可以用形容词，名词，或者动词ing
I was happy
You weren't at home
Was she eating?'''),
('Regular past tense verbs', '''Regular Past Tense Verbs 有规则的过去时

动词加ed
help + ed > helped
最后的字母是e的动词加ed
move + ed > moved
最后的字母是辅音加y的动词加ed
study + ed > studied'''),
('-ed pronunciation', '''怎么说"-ed"
单词最后的辅音是个清辅音加ed，ed听起来t
例子：helped，worked
单词最后的辅音是个浊辅音或者元音加ed，ed听起来d
例子：moved，tried*
单词最后的辅音是个t,d加ed，ed听起来ed
例子：hated，wanted

*去y加ied'''),
('Irregular past tense verbs', '''Irregular Past Tense Verbs 不规则的过去时

现在时- 过去时
run   - ran
come  - came
give  - gave
see   - saw
drink - drank
find  - found
get   - got(得到)
take  - took(拿)
forget- forgot(忘)
write - wrote
go    - went
fall  - fell(倒)
know  - knew(知道)
make  - made
put   - put(放)
eat   - ate
do    - did'''),
('Past tense questions', '''Past Tense Questions 过去时的问句

一般疑问句 Did ...?
Did you eat lunch?

wh-单词的问句 wh-单词 + did + ...?
Who did you see?
Where did you go?
What did you eat?'''),
('Could', '''Could 能的过去时

我昨天能看月了
I could see the moon yesterday

我去年不会骑自行车
Last year I couldn't ride a bike'''),
('Comparatives', '''Comparative Adjectives 比较级

more + 形容词 + than

仅添加er
quick - quicker
cheap - cheaper
This car is cheaper than that car.

有一些必须双写最后的辅音的单词
big - bigger
fat - fatter
The dog is bigger than the cat.

如果最后的字母是辅音加y,去y加ier
easy - easier
healthy - healthier
This game is easier than that game.

不能在长的形容词后面加er,反而在形容词前面放more
expensive - more expensive
dangerous - more dangerous
This road is more dangerous than the other road.

不规则的
good - better
bad - worse
This film is better than the other film.'''),
('One/ones', '''One/Ones 用来指已经提到的名词

one (单数)
Which pen do you want?
I want that one(指的是前述的pen)

ones (复数)
I like films.
I always watch really good ones(指的是前述的films)
''')),
