        (('Present simple', '''Present Simple 现在时

I/you/we/they eat
he/she/it eats
*如果个单词的最后的字母是s,x,ch,sh,o加es
I/you/we/they go
he/she/it goes
*如果个单词的最后的字母是辅音加y去y加ies
I/you/we/they study
he/she/it studies

否定句
不要改变否定句中的动词。在动词前加“don't”或“doesn't”
I don't eat
He doesn't eat
You don't study
She doesn't study

问句
不要改变问句中的动词。在动词前加“do”或“does”
Do you eat?
Does he study?
*否定的第三人称动词没有s,但是don't变成doesn't'''),
