('Be动词 past tense', '''Past Simple Be be动词的过去时

肯定句
I was...
You/we/they were...
he/she/it was...

否定句
I was not...
You/we/they were not...
he/she/it was not...

还有可能用be动词的缩写形式
I wasn't...
You/we/they weren't...
he/she/it wasn't...

问句
